'''C15''' is an untarred in eastern [[Namibia]] travelling 448km through the [[Khomas Region|Khomas]], [[Hardap Region|Hardap]], and [[ǁKaras Region]]s. It starts in [[Dordabis]] and ends at the [[Mata Mata, South Africa|Mata Mata]] border post, leading into [[South Africa]].


