==Sources== * Roald Amundsen told the story of the exploration of the Norwest Passage in two volumes entitled ''Die Nordwestpassage. Meine Polarfahrt mit der Gjöa 1903 - 1907''. the material was translated into English as ''The North-West Passage: Being the Record of a Voyage of Exploration of the ship "Gjøa" 1903-1907'' (Ams Press Inc; June 1908, {{ISBN|978-0-404-11625-5}} and reprinted Kessinger Pub Co, November 30, 2007, {{ISBN|978-0-548-77250-8}}). * [[Roland Huntford|Huntford, Roland]] (1999) ''The Last Place on Earth'' (Modern Library) {{ISBN|0-349-11395-5}} * Oterhals, Leo (2006) ''Havdrønn : om berømte båter og stolte båteiere'' (AS Lagunen) {{ISBN|82-90757-23-9}}
