{{marine-geo-stub}}

The '''High Commissioner of Niue to New Zealand''' is the top-ranking [[diplomatic representative]] of [[Niue]] to [[New Zealand]]. Niue is in [[Associated state|free association]] with New Zealand and lacks full [[sovereignty]]. New Zealand is the only country in the world in which Niue exchanges diplomatic representation.<ref name=rnzi>{{cite news |first=|last=|title=Niue appoints veteran woman politician as Wellington High Commissioner |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=58698 |work=[[Radio New Zealand International]] |publisher= |date=2011-02-10 |accessdate=2011-04-17}}</ref>

