==Future trips==
The following international trips are scheduled to be made by President Trump over the next several months. Additionally, the president has stated that he hopes to have a second [[2019 North Korea–United States summit|summit meeting]] with North Korean leader Kim Jong-un, as well as another meeting with Russian president Vladimir Putin in 2019.<ref>{{Cite web| title=Trump says second summit with Kim Jong Un will happen after the midterms| last=Sonmez| first=Felicia| url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-says-second-summit-with-kim-jong-un-will-happen-after-the-midterms/2018/10/09/4f58bd92-cc15-11e8-920f-dd52e1ae4570_story.html?noredirect=on&utm_term=.54c741610cac| work=Washington Post| date=October 9, 2018| access-date=November 8, 2018}}</ref>

